1.0.name: wordpress/d5-business-line
1.0.description: D5 Business Line is a theme for Small Business Companies. Customizable Background, Slide Images and other options will give the WordPress Driven Site an attractive look.  D5 Business Line is super elegant and Professional Theme which will create the business widely expressed.  Right and Footer Sidebar will be usable for showing the widgets and PlunIns items. Full Wide page can be used for showing showcase or other pages. D5 Creation's Support will be with you, Always!
